- A simple visualization lib for KDL::Chains..

- Requirements

KDL [a relatively recent version is required [SVN at Nov. 24, 2008]
Qt [Version 4 or greater with OpenGL support]

Qt is only required if you want to build the QKDLChainViewWidget

- Installation

./bootstrap.sh
./configure [your options here, see ./configure --help]
make 
make install

- Documentation

do

make doc

and point your browser to doc/html/index.html

- Comments, Patches, etc..

Send to Florian Schmidt (fschmidt@techfak.uni-bielefeld.de)

- Author

Florian Paul Schmidt (fschmidt@techfak.uni-bielefeld.de)
